{"title":"Loading竟然这样有趣","slug":"Loading竟然这样有趣","date":"2020-07-15T09:34:33.000Z","updated":"2020-07-15T09:34:33.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Loading竟然这样有趣.json","excerpt":null,"covers":["https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN/image/ambulanceloading.jpg"],"content":"<p>如今无论是在手机端还是PC端，浏览的页面的内容都会做的十分丰富，于是乎需要加载的东西就会很多。但是用户或许会网速慢或硬件卡，可能会遇到需要加载的情况，而没有耐心的人，就会因为不断的加载而放弃浏览直接关闭。</p>\n<p>于是添加一个有趣的Loading的画面，就可以大大地缓解等待过程的无趣感，让用户知道目前的加载状态，以及让用户多多关注在Loading画面的本身上，让他们把等待看成一件美好的事，那么我们来探寻一些有趣的Loading画面吧。</p>\n<div class=\"justified-gallery\"><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN/image/ambulanceloading.jpg\" alt=\"\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN/image/ballloading.gif\" alt=\"\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN/image/ballloading2.gif\" alt=\"\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN/image/ballonloading.gif\" alt=\"\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN/image/bigheadloading.gif\" alt=\"\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN/image/bikeloading2.gif\" alt=\"\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN/image/birdloading.gif\" alt=\"\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN/image/blockloading.gif\" alt=\"\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN/image/capsuleloading.gif\" alt=\"\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN/image/carloading.gif\" alt=\"\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN/image/catloading.gif\" alt=\"\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN/image/catloading2.gif\" alt=\"\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN/image/catloading3.gif\" alt=\"\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN/image/changeloading.gif\" alt=\"\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN/image/changeloading3.gif\" alt=\"\"><br><img src=\"http